  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Targeted Training on the Postural Control and Gross Motor Function in Children With Cerebral Palsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy of Targeted Training on the Postural Control and Gross Motor Function in Children With Cerebral Palsy</official_title>
